# Implementation Plan

Phase 0: Monorepo scaffold
Phase 1: krypton_core + adapter_jupiter (devnet)
Phase 2: AI harness + Level 2 flow
Phase 3: TanStack Start app + landing
Phase 4: Audit + keeper + Ika path
Phase 5: Mainnet private beta

## Done Log

### Phase 0 — Done (2026-06-15)
Monorepo scaffold: pnpm workspace, programs/krypton_core Anchor stub, packages (policy-schema, sdk, ui), services (orchestrator, krypton-sim-rs), ops Docker stub, CI workflow, README.

### Phase 3 — Done (2026-06-15)
TanStack Start app: landing, /docs, invite-gated /app, policy builder wizard, vault dashboard + NAV chart, Level 2 activity UI, policy detail route; style guide tokens applied.

### Agent session storage — Done (2026-06-24)
SQLite layer at `.data/krypton.db` with schema for sessions, cycles, vault registry, activity, and pending actions.
Service modules: session (24h TTL, 3/wallet cap), cycle (lease mutex), vault registry, activity events.

### Orchestrator package bootstrap — Done (2026-06-25)
Created `services/orchestrator` worker package with TypeScript build, root `pnpm orchestrator` entrypoint, and polling worker loop.
Implemented cycle FSM stages, stub-agent JSON outputs, and DB persistence for cycle runs, agent invocations, and permission-gated pending actions.

### Phase 2 — Done (2026-06-24)
Created `services/orchestrator` with a worker CLI that polls shared SQLite cycle jobs, leases one vault cycle at a time, and records cycle runs plus agent invocations.
Implemented the FSM through `PERMISSION_GATE`, default stub agents with structured JSON output, and Level 2 pending action creation for manual approval flow.

### Beta vertical slice — Done (2026-06-25)
Built multi-tenant API/service path from policy compile to vault creation/finalization, plus cycle queue and activity endpoints backed by SQLite.
Wired `/app/create`, `/app`, and `/app/vault/[id]` to real service handlers and on-chain transaction bundle flow, and validated with a passing production build.
